00:20:17.588 --> 00:20:18.988
Yes, sir!

261
00:20:18.988 --> 00:20:21.988
Hey, fantastic. Let's give it our best shot.

262
00:20:21.988 --> 00:20:23.088
Yes.

263
00:20:40.488 --> 00:20:44.188
I wonder if I don't have the knack for baseball?

264
00:20:44.188 --> 00:20:45.988
It's not that.

265
00:20:45.988 --> 00:20:49.988
Don't give up and practice more and more.

266
00:20:49.988 --> 00:20:53.288
If you give up before doing anything, that's it.

267
00:20:53.288 --> 00:20:56.688
