280
00:21:48.388 --> 00:21:50.488
No matter what...

281
00:21:50.488 --> 00:21:52.788
No matter what, don't ever give up!

282
00:21:52.788 --> 00:21:54.288
Yes, sir...

283
00:22:03.388 --> 00:22:06.188
So I really think,

284
00:22:06.188 --> 00:22:08.588
that the effort I put in back then was worth it.

285
00:22:08.588 --> 00:22:11.588
I feel that one should never give up.

286
00:22:11.588 --> 00:22:15.588
Really? Koshien is really a good place.

287
00:22:29.588 --> 00:22:33.588
